'''Furry Hideout''' is one of the most popular furry VRChat worlds out there, created by Lt_shadow.

It was created in the year 2021 and 2022, its glory laid in the huge mansion in the center of the map, surrounded by rocks and an ocean, this instance was getting updates almost every month, for different seasons such as, Halloween, Christmas, and other events like the vrc mouse expedition that was in 2024. In 2025 Furry hideout had a massive Halloween update where the map was decorated with various Halloween decorations and a fantastic spooky vibe with fake body bags, A massive spider and a creepy critical ring! After Halloween the hideout experienced a pinch of Christmas with a beautiful Christmas update which had a big tree, tinsel and other beautiful decorations. Furry hideout also features furry avatars for new furry fandom members who haven't yet acquired they're own avatar! Furry hideout is by far the heart and soul of the furry VRChat community.